new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
pos_neg_dict={}
pos_neg_len_dict={}
a=[]
b=[]
for i,j in zip(kys,new_cols):
    pos=datanov_diff[datanov_diff[j]>0]
    a.append(pos)
    b.append(len(pos))
    neg=datanov_diff[datanov_diff[j]<0]
    a.append(neg)
    b.append(len(neg))
    zro=datanov_diff[datanov_diff[j]==0]
    a.append(zro)
    b.append(len(zro))
    pos_neg_dict.update({i:a})
    pos_neg_len_dict.update({i:b})
    a=[]
    b=[]

new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Ratio","Total_Confirmed_Ratio","Daily_Recovered_Ratio","Total_Recovered_Ratio","Daily_Deceased_Ratio","Total_Deceased_Ratio"]
existing_cols=list(datanov_ratio_with_precision.columns)
existing_cols.pop(0)
existing_cols
prv_vals=[46730,8182819,58316,7489060,467,121557]
prv_vals=pd.DataFrame(prv_vals)
for i,j,l in zip(new_cols,existing_cols,range(0,len(prv_vals))):
    datanov_ratio_with_precision[i]=list(range(len(datanov_ratio_with_precision)))
    datanov_ratio_with_precision[i][0]=round(datanov_ratio_with_precision[j][0]/prv_vals[0][l],2)
    tmp=[]
    tmp.append(datanov_ratio_with_precision[i][0])
    for k in range(0,len(datanov_ratio_with_precision)-1):
        tmp.append(round(datanov_ratio_with_precision[j][k+1]/datanov_ratio_with_precision[j][k],2))
    datanov_ratio_with_precision[i]=tmp
